Revision history for Perl extension Tk::DBI::LoginDialog.

1.006	Thu, Oct 20, 2016 12:39:47 AM
	- Fixed button hard-naming in login (retry) routine.
	- cutover tests to standardised harness to avoid duplicate code.
	- amended POD for button label overrides.
	- fixed missing DESTROY routine in harness
	- more testing of button labelling

1.005	Tue, Jan 26, 2016  1:01:58 AM
	- Fixed Bug #108406
	- added -pressed property to allow polling of pressed button
	- advertises Label widgets in-case of requirement for relabelling
	- subordinated the DBI login routine to its own connect() function
	- added a disconnect() function
	- allow button labels to be changed with dynamic polling of buttons in cb_login

1.004	Fri, Oct 17, 2014  7:00:28 AM
	- changed geometry management to FORM for credentialling widgets
	- added version widget
	- more feedback from CPAN Testing

1.003	Mon, Oct 13, 2014  7:24:19 PM
	- tweaks from CPAN Testing and CPANTS
	- added version method
	- removed MANIFEST.SKIP which is causing packaging issues

1.002  Fri, Sep 19, 2014  5:42:48 AM
	- corrected "o" versus "self" in Populate
	- additional unit tests, particularly of SUPER/Subwidget properties
	- added some minimal perl/module version dependencies
	- tweaks from CPAN Testing and CPANTS

1.001  Sun May  5 09:27:29 2013
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-AX --skip-exporter --use-new-tests -n Tk::DBI::LoginDialog

